    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3, a purist\u2019s choice featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a 6-speed manual transmission. This unit maintains exceptional throttle response thanks to its individual throttle bodies and a flat torque curve that shines towards the 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis dynamics are sharp, supported by M-variable differential lock and multi-link rear suspension geometry that provides communicative feedback through the corners. Preventative maintenance on the rod bearings has been performed, ensuring the longevity of the high-strung internals. While the exterior shows honest patina from spirited driving, the powertrain remains robust with no signs of oil consumption or VANOS rattle.",
