    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a well-cared-for vehicle that presents beautifully and drives with confidence. The exterior paint retains a deep, reflective shine, complemented by clean alloy wheels and tires with significant tread life remaining. While the body is largely straight and impressive, there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small, superficial scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical of a car that has been enjoyed but respected. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean. The leather upholstery remains soft and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All interior electronics, from the high-fidelity audio system to the ice-cold dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; it has a documented service history showing regular oil changes and recent brake pad replacements. The engine runs smoothly without any odd noises, and the transmission delivers crisp, seamless shifts. This is a solid, reliable example that bridges the gap between a showroom piece and a dependable daily driver.",
